description:
Racing the Storm    Aired on 09/03/2003, Narrated by Stephen Bogaert
On 1 June 1999, American Airlines Flight 1420, a McDonnell Douglas MD-82, tries to land at the Little Rock National Airport during a storm, but overruns the runway, killing eleven people. The crash was caused by the crew not arming the spoilers during their pre-landing checks.
